# Module 2: Zscaler Architecture

## Overview
Zscaler architecture is built as a cloud-native, globally distributed platform that delivers security as a service. It eliminates the need for traditional data center-based security.

---

## 🔑 Key Concepts
- Multi-tenant cloud architecture
- Globally distributed data centers
- Security enforcement in the cloud
- No need for traffic backhauling

---

## 🌍 Core Components

### Zscaler Cloud
- Central platform where all security processing happens
- Hosted across multiple global data centers

### Enforcement Nodes
- Inspect and secure user traffic
- Apply policies and security controls

